{
  "stem": "293.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You will get a visa at this day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on the day of my birthday, he gave me a present visa for Mila and me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And April 17, or 10, or 17, we went to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have the $10, and Mila has $10 in the pocket.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only money we have.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was making $200 a month from UNRRA, but not the American dollars.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only the-- I could buy a pack of cigarettes for this $200.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were supposed to get paid in American dollars, but somebody was stealing the dollars, replacing with the-- the-- the-- the, you know--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the-- the-- thank you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when I came over on the boat, the captain, and the doctor, and one officer need four guys to play bridge.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they found me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I played bridge with them for the five nights that we were there, and I landed with $105 in Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was my fortune.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we stay in New York.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I open a business with the same friend, what we came from Budapest and things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was a year ahead in America than me because he has a brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he was working for an importer of leather goods from Argentina.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he told him that his cousin is coming who is a specialist in this field.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never knew it, how to open the handbag.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when I was introduced to him, and he said to me, you know how to repair bags?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Look, I was mechanics.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was a welder.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, I can repair anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I start-- they hire me, too, and I start working.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we decide to open a repair shop.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because he was sending repairs to another place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the guy charged a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
